could be stolen.

52:05.430 --> 52:06.660
As you can see in the video,

52:06.860 --> 52:08.770
his true sentiments
came to light.

52:08.970 --> 52:10.980
He will be deported
immediately.

52:11.180 --> 52:12.860
It is a bad day for the
Kremlin,

52:13.060 --> 52:15.460
